In [56]:
databymonth['STATE/UT'].unique()
This Dataset contains few duplicate names for some states and that creates inconsistency in dataset. For
Example : Dadra & Nagar Haveli has data with two dierent name 'D & N Haveli' and 'D&N Haveli'. We need
to x such discrepancies before analysis. These are small data issues, let's x them inside data les.
